headline: AM Best Affirms Credit Ratings of Quanta Insurance Company, Inc.
summary: OLDWICK, N.J., July 11, 2025--AM Best has affirmed the Financial Strength Rating of A- (Excellent) and the Long-Term Issuer Credit Rating of "a-" (Excellent) of Quanta Insurance Company, Inc. (QIC) (Houston, TX). The outlook of these Credit Ratings (ratings) is stable.
